item.title: The End
item.author: shawn.graham@carleton.ca (Dr. Shawn Graham)
item.description: Goals for this week this that the other thing Read Nothing to read this week. Do Finish your case study. Submit both to the OTTGlam github repo (ie, use the form below to send me the link to your work) Write your Exit Ticket With tech work, if it doesn’t come together in about 30 minutes, it won’t come in an hour. So take a break. Close the laptop.
